                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-46-defend325 t18020428-46-punish248"></join>
               Fined 1s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
